channel.title: RubSca - RELEASED! [Economy based + anti SYI]
channel.description:
[size=15pt]RubSca - Economy Server[/size] [url=http://www.megaupload.com/?d=GEHIWBG0]Download the server [ Uppit ][/url] [url=http://www.megaupload.com/?d=GEHIWBG0]Download the client [ MegaUpload ][/url]
Please recognize the time,and respect for MoparScape for me to release this very big project.
[b]Information about the server..[/b] The server is ran on a dedicated server,and Im getting really tired of it. Everyone who plays it loves it, and there is a daily average of a nonstop 30 players online. The server is [b]ECONOMY[/b] based! This means that this is built to be a long term server! Do not use this source if your looking to host it for 1 day, or have a cool pking server!
This server was based off of [b]DeltaScape[/b]. This server is a mixture of Dodian/Delta - It is very fun!
[b]Credits[/b] 50% - Delta (For the source base) :) 25% - Tonypker13 (Owner and Coder) :) 25% - BankHead/RSCReborn (Dedicated host and coder) :)
[b]The stability, reliable-ness[/b] We had 40+ Online for 2 1/2 weeks straight, with less than 2 crashes.
[b]Skills, and other information[/b] [u]EVERY SKILL WORKS![/u] You can use ANY skill, and do any of the 15 quests! This server is very very very stable,clean,and based upon the economy. There is a quest log, with actual rewards,requirements,and nice dialogues!
[b]Magicz[/b] Working 100% Every default spell Lunar / Vengeance Ancients / Barrage
[b]Special Attackz[/b] Real timers, actual effects and bonuses. DDS Has a good timer, good GFX display and has a bonus for the special.
[b]There are 4 staff levels[/b] *POWERS LISTED BELOW* 1)Moderator - Has the powers listed below 2)Admin - Cannot trade or drop items 3)Owner - Can trade and drop items
[b]Admins[/b] Working IPBan Working IPMute - Permanently mutes this IP from speaking Working Temp mute - 48 hour mute Working Perm mute - Permanent mute *[u]Note[/u]* - When admins die they do [b]NOT[/b] lose their items, even while pking!
[b]Moderators[/b] Working Temp mute Working Perm mute Working moderator panel (Report abuse) Leaves option to 48 hour or permanent mute. *[u]Note[/u]* - When moderators die they do [b]WILL[/b] lose their items, in all situations!
[b]Features[/b] Rubik's Features: -Fight Pits -Barrows -Full Pest Control -15 working quests -No lag -Over 70 people on daily -Many Train areas -Great economy base -Much more -ANTI SYIPKPKER + FLOODERS
[b]The starting items[/b]
[ul][li]Bronze Sword[/li] [li]Wooden Sheild[/li] [li]100 Bronze Arrowsv [/li][li]Shortbow[/li] [li]100 Lobsters[/li] [li]3,000 Gold[/li][/ul]
[b]Some commands[/b]
[ul][li]::Players (There are ** Players online!)[/li] [li]::Changepassword (You can change your password)[/li] [li]::yell [Global/Yell][/li] [li]::hail (For admins) Makes everyone say WE LOVE "Admin name"[/ul]
*Not many commands, hence this is a economy based server *There is not much use for commands
[b]Understanding the server[/b] When you login, you will be prompted to a customization screen (Design your character) You will have the starter items, etc. To get around the game you use your magic spells, All the teleports will bring you somewhere free of charge and spells.
[b]How to support this release[/b] If you have any trouble, you can always contact BankHead on MSN Email = xWillySupax@Hotmail.Com
[b]Server Downloads *Incase you cannot see them elsewere*[/b] [url=http://uppit.com/NOMFN3]Download server source [ Uppit ][/url] Http://uppit.com/NOMFN3 [code]Http://uppit.com/NOMFN3[/code]
[b]Client Downloads *Incase you cannot see them elsewere*[/b] [url=http://www.megaupload.com/?d=GEHIWBG0]Download Client[/url] Http://www.megaupload.com/?d=GEHIWBG0 [code]Http://www.megaupload.com/?d=GEHIWBG0[/code]
[b]Now, pictures of the server![/b]
